rx.internal.operators

类 DeferredScalarSubscriberSafe<T,R>

  • java.lang.Object
    • rx.Subscriber<T>
      • rx.internal.operators.DeferredScalarSubscriber<T,R>
        • rx.internal.operators.DeferredScalarSubscriberSafe<T,R>
  • 类型参数:
    T - source value type
    R - result value type
    所有已实现的接口:
    Observer<T>, Subscription

    public abstract class DeferredScalarSubscriberSafe<T,R>
extends DeferredScalarSubscriber<T,R>
    Supplements DeferredScalarSubscriber with defensive behaviour that ensures no emissions occur after a terminal event. If onError is called more than once then errors after the first are reported to RxJavaHooks.onError.

      • onError

        public void onError(java.lang.Throwable ex)
        从接口复制的说明: Observer
        Notifies the Observer that the Observable has experienced an error condition.

        If the Observable calls this method, it will not thereafter call Observer.onNext(T) or Observer.onCompleted().

        指定者:
        onError 在接口中 Observer<T>
        覆盖:
        onError 在类中 DeferredScalarSubscriber<T,R>
        参数:
        ex - the exception encountered by the Observable

      • onCompleted

        public void onCompleted()
        从接口复制的说明: Observer
        Notifies the Observer that the Observable has finished sending push-based notifications.

        The Observable will not call this method if it calls Observer.onError(java.lang.Throwable).

        指定者:
        onCompleted 在接口中 Observer<T>
        覆盖:
        onCompleted 在类中 DeferredScalarSubscriber<T,R>
